.SH NAME
.PP
monospace-cache-clear - Clear task cache


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBmonospace cache clear [task...] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Remove cache entries for the given tasks.

.PP
Without arguments, clears the entire cache (will prompt for confirmation unless
--force is set). With arguments (in project#task form), only those tasks are cleared.


.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB-f\fP, \fB--force\fP[=false]
	Skip confirmation when clearing all cache

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for clear


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
.PP
\fB-C\fP, \fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable color output mode (you can also use env var NO_COLOR)


